  "title": "Lashing Specialist",
  "description": "<p>The role of a Stevedore Cargo Master is to perform lashing/Unlashing operations on board vessels, vessel berthing/unberthing operations, plugging/unplugging operations, and water bunkering operations at PSA Container Terminal.<br /><br /><u><em>Salary Package Includes: Basic Salary + Overtime Pay (OT) + Meal Incentive + Transport Incentive + Other Allowances & Performance Incentives Location: PSA Port, Pasir Panjang.</em></u><br /></p><p><u><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><p>•Responsible for the positioning and securing of containers on board.</p><p>•Ensure smooth operations and safety compliance.</p><p>•Operate lashing gears safely following SOP.</p><p>•Other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</p><p>•Follow all safety rules and procedures.</p><p><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><p>•No experience needed <strong>(training provided!)</strong></p><p>•Able to work at heights is a plus</p><p>•Willing to work on rotating shifts and outdoors</p><p></p>",
